# To-Do List Application

## Author
vishnuvardhan s
## Description
This is a simple To-Do List application built using Python and Tkinter. It provides an intuitive GUI for users to manage their tasks efficiently.

## Features
-  **Add, View, and Delete Tasks**: Users can add new tasks, view their task list, and delete tasks when completed.
- **Persistent Storage**: Tasks are saved in a text file (`tasks.txt`) so they remain available even after closing the application.
-  **Error Handling**: Prevents empty task entries and invalid deletions.

## Installation and Usage

### **Requirements**
Ensure you have **Python 3** installed on your system.

### **Steps to Run the Application**
1. **Clone the Repository**  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/todo-list.git
   cd todo-list
